subject: Hello
body:
Hello
How are you doing today? I have a business proposal for you and I will
like us to
discuss more so that I can give you more details. It is 100% legal.

subject: Re:   Hello
body:
Hello Tom,

I'm doing well, thank you. I'm intrigued by your business proposal. Could you please provide more details about it?

Best wishes,
Luz
